    <title>iGraph 学习笔记（1）</title>
    <link href="https://www.notes.worstone.cn/2020/11/03/iGraph%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <id>https://www.notes.worstone.cn/2020/11/03/iGraph%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</id>
    <published>2020-11-03T06:08:50.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-11-03T06:09:50.883Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="iGraph学习笔记"><a href="#iGraph学习笔记" class="headerlink" title="iGraph学习笔记"></a>iGraph学习笔记</h1><h2 id="1-windows下安装"><a href="#1-windows下安装" class="headerlink" title="1.windows下安装"></a>1.windows下安装</h2><p>1.下载对应版本igraph的whl文件和pycario的whl文件</p><p>2.进入文件目录，使用命令行命令 pip install <del>~</del>，将两个文件安装</p><p>3.测试代码test.py：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from igraph import *</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">*g &#x3D; Graph.Famous(&quot;petersen&quot;)*</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">*plot(g)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果图：</p><p><img src="C:\Users\HP\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20201102172144213.png" alt="image-20201102172144213"></p><h2 id="2-创建图"><a href="#2-创建图" class="headerlink" title="2.创建图"></a>2.创建图</h2><h3 id="1-创建无顶点-边的无向图："><a href="#1-创建无顶点-边的无向图：" class="headerlink" title="1.创建无顶点/边的无向图："></a>1.创建无顶点/边的无向图：</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> igraph</span><br><span class="line">g = igraph.Graph()</span><br><span class="line">print(g)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出结果：IGRAPH U— 0 0 –     两个0分别表示顶点数和边数，–后应为图形名称（现在还未添加）</p><h3 id="2-添加、删除顶点和边："><a href="#2-添加、删除顶点和边：" class="headerlink" title="2.添加、删除顶点和边："></a>2.添加、删除顶点和边：</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">g.add_vertices(<span class="number">3</span>)<span class="comment">#添加顶点，序号从0开始</span></span><br><span class="line">g.add_edges([(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>), (<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>)])<span class="comment">#添加边</span></span><br><span class="line">g.add_edges([(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)])</span><br><span class="line">g.add_vertices(<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">g.add_edges([(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>), (<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>), (<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>), (<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">3</span>)])</span><br><span class="line">print(g)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出结果：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">IGRAPH U--- <span class="number">6</span> <span class="number">7</span> --</span><br><span class="line">+ edges:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0</span>-<span class="number">-1</span> <span class="number">1</span>-<span class="number">-2</span> <span class="number">0</span>-<span class="number">-2</span> <span class="number">2</span>-<span class="number">-3</span> <span class="number">3</span>-<span class="number">-4</span> <span class="number">4</span>-<span class="number">-5</span> <span class="number">3</span>-<span class="number">-5</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可见生成了6顶点7边的无向图。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">g.get_eid(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>)<span class="comment">#获取边的id， 输出： 3</span></span><br><span class="line">g.delete_edges(<span class="number">3</span>)<span class="comment">#删除边（id），</span></span><br><span class="line">summary(g)<span class="comment">#类似print，但不输出边的列表</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#输出：</span></span><br><span class="line">IGRAPH U--- <span class="number">6</span> <span class="number">6</span> --</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-生成图形："><a href="#3-生成图形：" class="headerlink" title="3.生成图形："></a>3.生成图形：</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>g = Graph.Tree(<span class="number">127</span>, <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>summary(g)</span><br><span class="line">IGRAPH U--- <span class="number">127</span> <span class="number">126</span> --</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Graph.Tree()生成规则树图，如上代码生成了127个顶点，每个顶点有2个子节点，且只要使用参数相同，生成的图始终相同。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>g = Graph.GRG(<span class="number">100</span>, <span class="number">0.2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>summary(g)</span><br><span class="line">IGRAPH U---- <span class="number">100</span> <span class="number">516</span> --</span><br><span class="line">+ attr: x (v), y (v)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Graph.GRG()生成几何随机图，+atrr表示顶点和边的属性名称</p><p>isomorhpic()可以判断两个图是否同构</p><h3 id="4-设置和检索属性："><a href="#4-设置和检索属性：" class="headerlink" title="4.设置和检索属性："></a>4.设置和检索属性：</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>g = Graph([(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>), (<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">2</span>), (<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>), (<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>), (<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">2</span>), (<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">5</span>), (<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">0</span>), (<span class="number">6</span>,<span class="number">3</span>), (<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">6</span>)])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>g.vs</span><br><span class="line">&lt;igraph.VertexSeq <span class="built_in">object</span> at <span class="number">0x1b23b90</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>g.vs[<span class="string">&quot;name&quot;</span>] = [<span class="string">&quot;Alice&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;Bob&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;Claire&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;Dennis&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;Esther&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;Frank&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;George&quot;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>g.vs[<span class="string">&quot;age&quot;</span>] = [<span class="number">25</span>, <span class="number">31</span>, <span class="number">18</span>, <span class="number">47</span>, <span class="number">22</span>, <span class="number">23</span>, <span class="number">50</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>g.vs[<span class="string">&quot;gender&quot;</span>] = [<span class="string">&quot;f&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;m&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;f&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;m&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;f&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;m&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;m&quot;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>g.es[<span class="string">&quot;is_formal&quot;</span>] = [<span class="literal">False</span>, <span class="literal">False</span>, <span class="literal">True</span>, <span class="literal">True</span>, <span class="literal">True</span>, <span class="literal">False</span>, <span class="literal">True</span>, <span class="literal">False</span>, <span class="literal">False</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>vs表示顶点顺序，es表示边的顺序，可以使用es[id]的形式修改单个属性，</p><h3 id="5-布局和绘图"><a href="#5-布局和绘图" class="headerlink" title="5.布局和绘图"></a>5.布局和绘图</h3><h4 id="布局算法"><a href="#布局算法" class="headerlink" title="布局算法"></a>布局算法</h4><p><em>igraph</em>中的布局方法可以在<code>Graph</code>对象中找到，并且它们始终以开头<code>layout_</code>。下表总结了它们：</p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">方法名称</th><th align="left">简称</th><th align="left">算法说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_circle</code></td><td align="left"><code>circle</code>， <code>circular</code></td><td align="left">确定性布局，将顶点放置在一个圆上</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_drl</code></td><td align="left"><code>drl</code></td><td align="left">大图的<a href="http://www.cs.sandia.gov/~smartin/software.html">分布式递归布局</a>算法</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_fruchterman_reingold</code></td><td align="left"><code>fr</code></td><td align="left">Fruchterman-Reingold力导向算法</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_fruchterman_reingold_3d</code></td><td align="left"><code>fr3d</code>， <code>fr_3d</code></td><td align="left">三维Fruchterman-Reingold力导向算法</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_grid_fruchterman_reingold</code></td><td align="left"><code>grid_fr</code></td><td align="left">具有大网格图启发式的Fruchterman-Reingold力导向算法</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_kamada_kawai</code></td><td align="left"><code>kk</code></td><td align="left">Kamada-Kawai力导向算法</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_kamada_kawai_3d</code></td><td align="left"><code>kk3d</code>， <code>kk_3d</code></td><td align="left">三维Kamada-Kawai力导向算法</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_lgl</code></td><td align="left"><code>large</code>， <code>lgl</code>， <code>large_graph</code></td><td align="left"><a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/lgl/">大图</a>的<a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/lgl/">大图布局</a>算法</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_random</code></td><td align="left"><code>random</code></td><td align="left">将顶点完全随机地放置</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_random_3d</code></td><td align="left"><code>random_3d</code></td><td align="left">将顶点完全随机地放置在3D中</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_reingold_tilford</code></td><td align="left"><code>rt</code>， <code>tree</code></td><td align="left">Reingold-Tilford树的布局，对（几乎）树状图很有用</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_reingold_tilford_circular</code></td><td align="left"><code>rt_circular``tree</code></td><td align="left">具有极坐标后变换的Reingold-Tilford树布局，对（几乎）树状图很有用</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>layout_sphere</code></td><td align="left"><code>sphere</code>， <code>spherical</code>， <code>circular_3d</code></td><td align="left">确定性布局，可将顶点均匀地放置在球体的表面上</td></tr></tbody></table><p>布局算法可以直接调用，也可以使用常见的布局方法调用 <code>layout()</code>：</p><h4 id="使用布局绘图"><a href="#使用布局绘图" class="headerlink" title="使用布局绘图"></a>使用布局绘图</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt; layout &#x3D; g.layout(&quot;kk&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt; plot(g, layout &#x3D; layout)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="C:\Users\HP\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20201102185730449.png" alt="image-20201102185730449"></p><p>使用Kamada-Kawai布局算法绘制，效果如图。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
